{"tid":2325768,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA宣布：James Webb太空望遠鏡，將延後7個月發射","createTime":"2020-12-15T00:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T11:44:17.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94e0ecf7eaf9aa1ad751d7294aabcbb3e8cb101a","tid":2325768,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"由於COVID-19疫情的影響，以及技術上面臨的挑戰，美國國家航空暨太空總署（NASA）將再次延後詹姆斯&middot;韋伯太空望遠鏡的發射時間。NASA預計於2021年10月31日，在法國屬地圭亞那發射詹姆斯&middot;韋伯太空望遠鏡。<br />\n<br />\n此計畫源於1996年的「新世代太空望遠鏡」（Next Generation Space Telescope，NGST）計畫，當時預計斥資5億美元，於2007年發射。但隨著面臨的研發技術、製造工藝的挑戰，至今JWST的研發成本上看88億美元，整個計畫的預算也提升至96.6億美元。<br />\n<br />\n振動測試已定於 8 月開始。NASA 預計到 2021 年年初，這個網球場大小的望遠鏡將摺疊起來運送到發射場，然後將其安裝到亞利安 5 號火箭整流罩中進行發射。<br />\n<br />\nJWST是有史以來最強大的太空望遠鏡，能捕捉大爆炸之後第一批恆星和星系的發出的光，提供科學家研究星系的形成與演化的資源。在未來它會與哈伯太空望遠鏡合作，拓展哈伯過去三十年的發現，使人類看見更遙遠的過去。<br />\n<br />\n延誤足足15年既計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2d7c885a09576ab0a007a3f26e78459fab09e7","tid":2325768,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:36:21.000Z","msg":"NASA點解唔用Spacex射上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdbbb66f7708ea0bd29e20a3d493dcc0653359f","tid":2325768,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d2d7c885a09576ab0a007a3f26e78459fab09e7","tid":2325768,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:36:21.000Z","msg":"NASA點解唔用Spacex射上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:40:25.000Z","msg":"因為一早就定好左，講緊既係20幾年前既事，呢個係同歐洲太空總處合作，當年計劃岩岩開始時已定好係由法國既亞利安5號火箭飛，係無諗過拖到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df14598a7ec64b71ad53566326c046ed492a0fb9","tid":2325768,"uid":129436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"拖到2046"},{"pid":"daa3569d627574f607f2b4670c11eb4105b01327","tid":2325768,"uid":342891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"紅外線唔會影可見光影像，<br />\n雖然因為紅移科學發現需要紅外線多一點，<br />\n但情感上因為冇可見光的相睇，<br />\n我就覺得冇乜好期待了。"},{"pid":"7f4c3d15eaae40d100a52c181c02979f465501ef","tid":2325768,"uid":343134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}